 it back to the breath for the remainder of your allotted practice and remember that there is no right or wrong way to do this. It is all about the experience and what you get out of it.\r\n<h4>Be (and stay) aware</h4>\r\nAs your practice continues begin to feel your awareness. Observe your awareness and how aware you are, despite your relatively calm state. The experience of pure awareness is much-prized in the art of meditation and the more you can cultivate it the more peace you will feel inside.\r\n<h4>End the session calmly</h4>\r\nDont finish your session by jumping up and rushing off to something else. Allow the calm and tranquillity to flow naturally into the rest of your day and you will find yourself acting more decisively, without the emotional conflicts that usually crop up during the hustle and bustle of a busy day. In this way, you can your meditation with you wherever you go.','Test 5','','inherit','closed','closed','','202-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:23:25','2017-01-16 14:23:25','',202,'http://demo4.saitobaza.ru/202-revision-v1.htm',0,'revision','',0),(318,2,'2017-01-16 17:30:23','2017-01-16 14:30:23','','','','publish','open','open','','prisedaniya','','','2017-01-16 17:30:23','2017-01-16 14:30:23','',0,'http://demo4.saitobaza.ru/?p=318',0,'post','',0),(319,2,'2017-01-16 17:30:23','2017-01-16 14:30:23','','','','inherit','closed','closed','','318-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:30:23','2017-01-16 14:30:23','',318,'http://demo4.saitobaza.ru/318-revision-v1.htm',0,'revision','',0),(320,2,'2017-01-16 18:06:34','2017-01-16 15:06:34','',' ','','publish','closed','closed','','trenirovochnye-programmy-2','','','2017-01-16 18:49:55','2017-01-16 15:49:55','',0,'http://demo4.saitobaza.ru/?page_id=320',0,'page','',0),(321,2,'2017-01-16 18:06:34','2017-01-16 15:06:34','',' ','','inherit','closed','closed','','320-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 18:06:34','2017-01-16 15:06:34','',320,'http://demo4.saitobaza.ru/320-revision-v1.htm',0,'revision','',0),(322,